fr.ign.cogit.cartagen.software.dataset

Class GeneObjImplementation

  • Object
    • GeneObjImplementation

  • public class GeneObjImplementation
extends Object
    A GeneObjImplementation instance informs on a particular implementation of the IGeneObj schema classes. A CartAGenDB only contains features from one of these implementations.
    Author:
    GTouya
